{"tid":1087004,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"教職員唔中意用canteen餐具","createTime":"2019-04-01T05:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T05:59:43.000Z","uid":185577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6a5d44af44ef694d2b2c9c707336d3b95356898a","tid":1087004,"uid":185577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:57:22.000Z","msg":"啱啱係九龍塘某U ac2 canteen買飯，有個男人叫左個雞飯加杯 芝士烏龍（幾好飲，呢排買一送一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   ：收錢呀姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：男人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：$42 蚊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：VISA (比完準備走)<br />\n                        ～返轉頭～<br />\n                         唔係跟餐加$6蚊？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：芝士吖嘛！芝士加$10蚊嫁！<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男人走左，又又又返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：有冇筷子餐具<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：先生出面有得自己攞，筷子匙扣係曬到，你唔係外賣冇得攞個喎<br />\n～經典黎啦～<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：個啲污糟呀。我係教職員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑向左右走死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係話環保撚，只係覺得佢個理由好好笑。<br />\n有滾水紙巾都唔識洗，何況我地啲低下階層，大菌食細菌，佢係入面點煮我都唔知啦&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n#我係教職員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n#如果佢答我唔支持環保我中意用新嘢我會比個like佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d4c216b06b6ba87a910bd18bb424a3d81c779e","tid":1087004,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:59:43.000Z","msg":"#原來如此，多謝分享"}]}